        "Dear Modupe,",
        "Trust you're well. I was over the moon to receive your letter, the icing on the cake was your IELTS result. Wow! You scored 9 overall? That's an incredible feat.",
        "I thought i'd let you know that i finally registered for my IELTS  after much delay. I will be sitting for the exam in September . I have also started preparations for the test. I spend approximately two hours each day after work practicing with the materials i got from Jay's website, remember the YouTube tutor i showed you? My scores in the reading section has improved greatly from 28 to 34, i plan to surpass that before test day.",
